### --- AUTHENTICATION ---

### Register User
POST http://localhost:5000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login User
POST http://localhost:5000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### --- SMART TRIP GENERATION ---

### Generate a 3-Day Trip to France (Budget: 5000)
# This will pick a city in France (Paris), find places within budget, and create the itinerary.
POST http://localhost:5000/itinerary/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": 9,
  "country_name": "France",
  "start_date": "2025-07-01",
  "end_date": "2025-07-03",
  "budget": 5000
}

### --- REVIEWS ---

### Add a Review for Eiffel Tower (place_id: 51)
POST http://localhost:5000/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": 9,
  "place_id": 51,
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "An absolute masterpiece of architecture! Must see at night."
}

### Get Reviews for a Place (place_id: 51)
GET http://localhost:5000/reviews/51

### --- CHATBOT ---

### Chatbot - Plan a 3-day trip in Tokyo
POST http://localhost:5000/chatbot
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "plan a 3 day trip in Tokyo"
}

### --- EXPLORE DATA ---

### Get All Countries
GET http://localhost:5000/countries

### Get Cities in Italy
GET http://localhost:5000/cities/IT

### Get Places in Rome (city_id: 21)
# You may need to check the cities list for the correct ID
GET http://localhost:5000/places/21

### Get Itinerary Details
# Replace {itinerary_id} with the ID from the "Generate Trip" response
GET http://localhost:5000/itinerary/details/1
